overview: Stuck in the New Town with dreams of becoming a pop star, never truly fitting in - aspirations bubbling away inside. A tunnel sneaking through the M25, a divider that is physical, political and socioeconomic - a fanaticism, a desire. Desperately trying to transform - no I don't wanna work a 9-5, I just wanna dress up and go out.
title: Signing On, Signing Off (Redux)
